# Multi-Niche Vision (Phase 2)

When the user asks to **expand to multiple niches**, **add a new niche**, or **follow the hub & spoke plan**, use **docs/CURSOR_RULES_MULTI_NICHE.md** and the full spec in **cursorrules (1)**.

**Current site:** Single-niche AI tools — flat routes (/compare, /tools, /blog).

**Target:** Hub & spoke — `/[niche]/...` with 6 niches:
1. AI Tools (`/ai-tools/`)
2. Web Hosting (`/web-hosting/`)
3. VPN (`/vpn/`)
4. eCommerce Tools (`/ecommerce-tools/`)
5. Marketing Tools (`/marketing-tools/`)
6. Online Courses (`/online-courses/`)

**Implement in this order:** Finish AI Tools as first niche, then add niches table and migrate routes to `/[niche]/compare`, `/[niche]/tools`, etc. Use config (niches.config.ts, affiliate.config.ts) — never hardcode niche data.
